#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/addon:2 input:9 standard
msgid "Editor: Height Tools"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"Adjust height for the whole map or apply heights to mountainous terrains "
"automatically"
msgstr ""
"Ajusteu l'alçada per a tot el mapa o apliqueu altures als terrenys "
"muntanyosos automàticament"

#. TRANSLATORS: Short for "set height to:"
#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:15 input:15 standard
msgid "Set to:"
msgstr "Estableix a:"

#. TRANSLATORS: Short for "lower height by"
#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:18 input:18 standard
msgid "Lower by:"
msgstr "Baixa per:"

#. TRANSLATORS: Short for "elevate height by"
#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:21 input:21 standard
msgid "Elevate by:"
msgstr "Elevar per:"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:42 input:42 standard
msgid ""
"A coordinate can't be read.\n"
"Make sure you have entered a valid coordinate in form of 20,34"
msgstr ""
"No es pot llegir una coordenada.\n"
"Assegureu-vos que heu introduït una coordenada vàlida en forma de 20,34"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:49 input:49 standard
msgid ""
"The coordinates exceeds the map height or width!\n"
"Please enter valid coordinates!"
msgstr ""
"Les coordenades superen l'alçada o l'amplada del mapa!\n"
"Introduïu les coordenades vàlides!"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:277 input:277 standard
msgid "Warning"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/auto_height.lua:278 input:278 standard
msgid ""
"This will change the height of %1$d fields! Approximately this last more "
"than %2$d sec.\n"
"The editor does not react for this time.\n"
"Click 'Cancel' to define a smaller area. Before clicking OK be sure to save "
"the map!"
msgstr ""
"Això canviarà l'alçada de %1$d camps! Aproximadament això dura més de %2$d "
"segons.\n"
"L'editor no reacciona per aquesta vegada.\n"
"Feu clic a \"Cancel·la\" per definir una àrea més petita. Abans de fer clic "
"a D'acord, assegureu-vos de desar el mapa!"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/error_window.lua:7 input:7 standard
msgid "Error"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/error_window.lua:28
#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:291 input:28 input:291
#: standard
msgid "OK"
msgstr "D'acord"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/init.lua:12 input:12 standard
msgid "Height Tools"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/init.lua:13 input:13 standard
msgid ""
"Set height for the whole map or apply heights to mountainous terrains "
"automatically"
msgstr ""
"Estableix l'alçada per a tot el mapa o apliqueu altures als terrenys "
"muntanyosos automàticament"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:14 input:14 standard
msgid "Choose an option"
msgstr "Trieu una opció"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:28 input:28 standard
msgid "Adjust height of all fields"
msgstr "Ajusteu l'alçada de tots els camps"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:43 input:43 standard
msgid "Set all fields to value"
msgstr "Estableix tots els camps en valor"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:47 input:47 standard
msgid "Lower all fields by value"
msgstr "Baixeu tots els camps per valor"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:51 input:51 standard
msgid "Elevate all fields by value"
msgstr "Eleva tots els camps per valor"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:63 input:63 standard
msgid "Set to: "
msgstr "Estableix a:"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:70 input:70 standard
msgid "Value for all fields"
msgstr "Valor per a tots els camps"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:86 input:86 standard
msgid "Adjust Height"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:96 input:96 standard
msgid "Apply random heights to mountain terrains"
msgstr "Aplicar altures aleatòries als terrenys de muntanya"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:104 input:104 standard
msgid ""
"Define a rectangular area by entering the coordinates of the top left corner "
"and the coordinates of the bottom right corner of the rectangle. Or define a "
"hexagonal area, like when using a big tool size, by entering the coordinates "
"of the center and a radius."
msgstr ""
"Definiu una àrea rectangular introduint les coordenades de la cantonada "
"superior esquerra i les coordenades de la cantonada inferior dreta del "
"rectangle. O definiu una àrea hexagonal, com quan utilitzeu una mida d'eina "
"gran, introduint les coordenades del centre i un radi."

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:105 input:105 standard
msgid ""
"The values for the coordinates can be found in the main menu panel on the "
"right side, e.g.: (20,&nbsp;52,&nbsp;10). The values represents (x-"
"coordinate,&nbsp;&nbsp;y-coordinate,&nbsp;height)"
msgstr ""
"Els valors de les coordenades es poden trobar al panell del menú principal a "
"la dreta, per exemple: (20,&nbsp;52,&nbsp;10). Els valors representen "
"(coordenada x,&nbsp;&nbsp;coordenada y,&nbsp;alçada)"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:111 input:111 standard
msgid "Global Options"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:125 input:125 standard
msgid "Max. Height:"
msgstr "Màx. Alçada:"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:126 input:126 standard
msgid "Restrict the height to this maximum height."
msgstr "Limiteu l'alçada a aquesta alçada màxima."

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:135 input:135 standard
msgid "Place sign"
msgstr "Senyal de lloc"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:136 input:136 standard
msgid "Place a column at given coordinates"
msgstr "Col·loca una columna a les coordenades donades"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:147 input:147 standard
msgid "Hexagonal Area"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:163 input:163 standard
msgid "Coordinates of the center field of the hexagonal area, e.g.: 20,35"
msgstr "Coordenades del camp central de l'àrea hexagonal, p. ex.: 20,35"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:171
#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:242
#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:271 input:171 input:242
#: input:271 standard
msgid "Enter coordinates in form of x, y"
msgstr "Introduïu les coordenades en forma de x, y"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:192 input:192 standard
msgid "Choose a value for the radius"
msgstr "Trieu un valor per al radi"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:210 input:210 standard
msgid "Random Hexagonal Mountains"
msgstr "Muntanyes hexagonals aleatòries"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:218 input:218 standard
msgid "Rectangular Area"
msgstr ""

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:234 input:234 standard
msgid "Coordinates of the top left corner of the rectangle, e.g.: 10,20"
msgstr ""
"Coordenades de la cantonada superior esquerra del rectangle, p. ex.: 10,20"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:263 input:263 standard
msgid "Coordinates of the bottom right corner of the rectangle, e.g.: 20,35"
msgstr ""
"Coordenades de la cantonada inferior dreta del rectangle, p. ex.: 20,35"

#: addons/editor_height_tools.wad/settings_window.lua:282 input:282 standard
msgid "Random Rectangular Mountains"
msgstr "Muntanyes rectangulars aleatòries"

#: input:3 screenshots/editor_height_tools.wad/descriptions:3 standard
msgid "Design your flat map and add some mountain terrains"
msgstr "Dissenya el teu mapa pla i afegeix alguns terrenys de muntanya"

#: input:4 screenshots/editor_height_tools.wad/descriptions:4 standard
msgid "Open the height tools, define a rectangular area and click on "
msgstr "Obriu les eines d'alçada, definiu una àrea rectangular i feu clic a"

#: input:5 screenshots/editor_height_tools.wad/descriptions:5 standard
msgid "Two signs are placed representing the given coordinates"
msgstr "Es col·loquen dos signes que representen les coordenades donades"

#: input:6 screenshots/editor_height_tools.wad/descriptions:6 standard
msgid ""
"The created mountain on the left doesn't look good? Enter the coordinates of "
"the center and click on "
msgstr ""
"La muntanya creada a l'esquerra no es veu bé? Introduïu les coordenades del "
"centre i feu clic a"

#: input:7 screenshots/editor_height_tools.wad/descriptions:7 standard
msgid ""
"You could also modify a mountain. Enter the coordinates of the new center "
"and click on "
msgstr ""
"També pots modificar una muntanya. Introduïu les coordenades del nou centre "
"i feu clic a"
